{"kind": "daily", "date": "2026-07-19", "html": "<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,'PingFang TC','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:#16213e;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a2b4a;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;padding-left:12px;margin:0 0 18px;\">📰 每日 AI 新聞 Top 10 · 2026-07-19</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eef4ff;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#5b8def;font-weight:800;\">1.</span> Dave Eggers Told OpenAI Staff That ChatGPT Was 'Silencing an Entire Generation'<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#3b6cf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">戴夫・艾格斯告訴OpenAI員工：ChatGPT正在「讓一整個世代噤聲」</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Author Dave Eggers gave a talk to about 200 OpenAI staffers, warning that ChatGPT could be stifling an entire generation's creative voice.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">作家戴夫・艾格斯受邀向約200名OpenAI員工演講，警告ChatGPT恐讓一整個世代的創作聲音消失。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/ai-artificial-intelligence/967630/dave-eggers-openai-chatgpt-silencing-an-entire-generation\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#ecf7ef;border-left:5px solid #4caf72;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#4caf72;font-weight:800;\">2.</span> Apple's Plot to Crush OpenAI<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#1e9e57;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">蘋果對OpenAI的反制計畫</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Apple has filed an intense lawsuit against OpenAI, and while many allegations reflect common industry practice, the fight signals a deeper strategic rivalry.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">蘋果對OpenAI提起措辭強烈的訴訟，儘管多項指控被視為業界常見做法，這場公開對決透露出雙方更深層的策略角力。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/podcast/967244/apple-openai-lawsuit-vergecast\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f1ecfb;border-left:5px solid #8a6bd8;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#8a6bd8;font-weight:800;\">3.</span> How Google's New Gemini Rates Work and How to Track Your Usage<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6b3bf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Google Gemini新計費制度解析與用量追蹤方式</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Google has changed how it tallies Gemini usage quotas, meaning users may get fewer AI responses than before.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Google調整了Gemini用量配額的計算方式，使用者可能會發現能用的AI回覆次數比以前更少。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Wired</b> · <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/how-googles-new-gemini-rates-work-and-how-to-track-your-usage/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f6f5;border-left:5px solid #2bb0a6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#2bb0a6;font-weight:800;\">4.</span> Vertu Wants Executives to Pay $6,880 for an AI Agent — Here's How It Actually Performs<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#0f9b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Vertu要價6,880美元推出「AI代理」手機，實測表現如何？</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">From AI workflows to battery life and security, Vertu's luxury foldable phone with a built-in AI agent gets put to the daily test.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">從AI工作流程、電池續航到安全性，實測Vertu這款內建AI代理的奢華折疊手機日常使用表現。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/17/vertu-wants-executives-to-pay-6880-for-an-ai-agent-heres-how-it-actually-performs/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fbf3e3;border-left:5px solid #d99b3f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#d99b3f;font-weight:800;\">5.</span> TikTok Is Testing an AI Likeness Detection Tool<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b9791f;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">TikTok測試AI肖像偵測工具</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">TikTok is piloting an opt-in tool that scans for AI-generated likenesses and lets creators report unauthorized uses to the company.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">TikTok正在測試一項可選加入的工具，用來偵測AI生成的肖像，並讓創作者向平台檢舉未經授權的使用情形。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/tech/967486/tiktok-ai-likeness-detection-tool\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fdeef0;border-left:5px solid #e0738a;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#e0738a;font-weight:800;\">6.</span> The Zoom Hack That Says, 'Don't Record Me'<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#d83a5e;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">一招對抗Zoom：「別錄我」的反制技巧</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">As meetings, conversations, and even dates increasingly get transcribed and AI-summarized, a new workaround pushes back against constant recording.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">隨著會議、對話甚至約會都被錄音並交由AI摘要，一項新技巧讓人們得以拒絕被全程記錄。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/17/the-zoom-hack-that-says-dont-record-me/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#edeefb;border-left:5px solid #6b72d6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#6b72d6;font-weight:800;\">7.</span> Patreon Stops Asking AI Bots Not to Scrape — and Starts Blocking Them<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#5159c9;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Patreon不再「拜託」AI爬蟲別抓資料，直接動手封鎖</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Patreon is teaming up with Cloudflare to actively block AI bots that scrape creator content for model training without permission.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Patreon與Cloudflare合作，主動封鎖未經授權、爬取創作者內容用於AI模型訓練的爬蟲程式。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/17/patreon-stops-asking-ai-bots-not-to-scrape-and-starts-blocking-them/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f4fb;border-left:5px solid #3f97c9;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#3f97c9;font-weight:800;\">8.</span> Agility Robotics Plants Its Flag in Tesla's Backyard<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#2b7fb0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Agility Robotics插旗特斯拉大本營</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Agility Robotics is opening a new training center for its Digit humanoid robots in Fremont, California — right where Tesla is based.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Agility Robotics在特斯拉總部所在地加州弗利蒙開設新訓練中心，用來培訓其人形機器人Digit。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/17/agility-robotics-plants-its-flag-in-teslas-backyard/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f2f6e8;border-left:5px solid #88a83f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#88a83f;font-weight:800;\">9.</span> A Scorecard for the AI Age<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6e8c28;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">研究</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">為AI時代打造一份成績單</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI CFO Sarah Friar proposes a practical scorecard to measure AI ROI through useful work completed, cost per successful task, and dependability.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI財務長Sarah Friar提出一套實用的AI投資報酬率衡量架構，涵蓋完成的有效工作量、單次任務成本與可靠度等指標。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">OpenAI</b> · <a href=\"https://openai.com/index/a-scorecard-for-the-ai-age\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">10.</span> Linus Torvalds Weighs In on Linux Kernel's Stance Toward AI<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Linus Torvalds談Linux核心對AI的立場</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Linux creator Linus Torvalds says the kernel project won't broadly reject AI tools, though human submitters must still review, verify licensing, and take full responsibility for the code.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Linux創始人Linus Torvalds表示，核心專案不會全面排斥AI工具，但人類提交者仍須審查程式碼、確認授權並承擔全部責任。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177381\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:#9aa1ad;padding-top:10px;\">由 AI News Digest 從各家 RSS 自動挑選、翻譯並寄送</div>\n</div>\n"}